Package src

Class Event

  • java.lang.Object
    • src.Event
  • public class Event
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used to create a Event object.

    The Event object contains the following:

    - A unique ID

    - A user ID of the user creates object

    - A title

    - A description

    - A date

    - A remind

    - A location

    - A duration

    - A priority

    - A list of participants

    Author:
    Sang Doan Tan 1370137
